Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600

Hide
Type 'PS1="> "' Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Sleep 100 ms
Show

Type "go run ./main.go export" Sleep 500ms  Enter
Sleep 4s

Down Sleep 750ms
Space Sleep 750ms
Down Sleep 750ms
Space Sleep 750ms
Down Sleep 750ms
Down Sleep 750ms
Space Sleep 3s

Enter
Sleep 6s
